What version of OS you have

$ cat /etc/redhat-release
CentOS Linux release 7.6.1810 (Core)

$ cat /etc/os-release
NAME="CentOS Linux"
VERSION="7 (Core)"
ID="centos"
ID_LIKE="rhel fedora"
