User  Management

# useradd
# usermod
# userdel
# useradd <uname>           
# passwd <uname>
# useradd -c "Comments"    <uname>
# usermod -l <new_name>    <old_name>
# usermod -u <new_id> <uname>
# userdel <uname>
# userdel --remove <uname>  
